message.content:
{
    "ocr_text": "F.R.G.B.

It might be well for you to suggest to such state correspondents as I herewith furnish you, for them to take the matter up with their constituencies in the cities of their states for endorsement and co-operation.

In this way we would be able to make greater headway in states that are progressive, than we would if we simply communicated with each locality in the state from any central point outside of the state.

Hoping that your efforts may meet with hearty approval, I am,

Very truly yours,

Sam'l Gompers
President
American Federation of Labor.",
    "summary": "The letter suggests state correspondents discuss issues with constituents for endorsement and cooperation to make greater progress. It is signed by Sam Gompers, President of the American Federation of Labor.",
